          }
        },
        "text_Tgm7iC": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Explore Bourne’s range of stylish and durable toilets, basins, vanities, and baths, designed to bring lasting quality and contemporary elegance to your bathroom. Whether you’re renovating or building new, Bourne offers practical solutions with modern designs that elevate your space with comfort and functionality.</p>"
